    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >STILLAE 精英战士由 Sanguis of the Mater 孕育而生，他们肩负着最后的神圣希望，等待你带领他们通过战斗拯救一个垂死的世界。与“停滞”势力展开战术对抗，恢复生命的流转！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >完美规划</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在动态回合制战斗中，精心策划你的后续行动，在战场上策略性地触发史诗级连锁事件：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用时间轴效应来加速、延迟或交换时间位置，从而影响回合顺序，智胜敌人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用可以爆炸、引燃敌人或阻挡视野的环境元素…扭转战局走向</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >借助击退、强制转向、侧翼攻击加成和持续伤害等空间效应，主宰每场战斗。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁丰富的能力库，每种能力都提供强大的协同效应并可进行深度自定义构建。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275050/extras/de1fb7a63413efe9ccb6fde7dd83313b.poster.avif?t=1771952211\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275050/extras/de1fb7a63413efe9ccb6fde7dd83313b.webm?t=1771952211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275050/extras/de1fb7a63413efe9ccb6fde7dd83313b.mp4?t=1771952211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >承担风险，不断前进</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在地图上选择你自己的道路和难度。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接受高风险、高回报的任务，直面头目战；或者放慢脚步收集资源以提高成功几率。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有任务都会推动渐进式游戏进度，并反映你所选择的体验类型。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275050/extras/da4ea578a2e712485a0903677790946a.poster.avif?t=1771952211\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275050/extras/da4ea578a2e712485a0903677790946a.webm?t=1771952211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275050/extras/da4ea578a2e712485a0903677790946a.mp4?t=1771952211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >适合回合制战斗的轻度 Rogue 循环</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过结合随机掉落的技能和你独特的装备配置，在你的 STILLAE 之间产生不同的协同效应。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重复挑战随机生成的关卡，扩大你的 Sanguine 影响力，击败独特的头目，并了解“停滞”的世界。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >失败并非终点，即使死亡也能取得进度，Mater 将再次召唤她的孩子们。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >猩红起义</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个被“净化”之力榨干的世界里，鲜血即是反抗。每一滴鲜血都将世界染成红与黑，提醒着人们生命正在反击。这不仅仅是暴力，它是在一个苍白无色的世界中，对那些想让世界永远陷入停滞的势力发起的一场鲜活起义。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275050/extras/2ded69df640704357479484a383a4be1.poster.avif?t=1771952211\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275050/extras/2ded69df640704357479484a383a4be1.webm?t=1771952211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275050/extras/2ded69df640704357479484a383a4be1.mp4?t=1771952211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
